overview.en: VETH is a global leading traceability block chain platform based on block chains and Internet of Things technology. It also established a wine traceability brewing estate based on block chain technology in the United States as the first application of the project.
overview.zh: VETH是加速世界向商业应用型的区块链网络转变，VETH正在构建一个以太坊侧链平台，我们定义并实现了VETH内核，它包含一个区块链系统需要的最基础的功能，也就是最小化区块链系统。
